{"tid":633961,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"試過喺舊登/連登發掘左咩冷門少少既動漫？","createTime":"2018-04-18T18:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T08:16:07.000Z","uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"207333ec0f5199c540262f9da67cc677b4f02c6c","tid":633961,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"有時睇返d求漫畫名既post/推介post就會唔小心墜左坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係呢啲post,我都唔會開始睇呢類動漫，尤其係重口蘿莉漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲冷門漫好多時都冇好好收尾，但佢個開頭至中段真係好撚引人入勝，唔捨得唔追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得既有：<br />\n校舍的後方埋藏著天使<br />\n痴撚線小學欺凌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/021419_24e9619ad9336d32c8e6c3873fb09574.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F021419_24e9619ad9336d32c8e6c3873fb09574.png&h=fcf2974c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不為世人認可的我僅能為杏奈所做的一點事<br />\n人渣男主回到過去搞大蘿莉個肚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/021600_1703083216baf48a7cf0dfcd67aa1a50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F021600_1703083216baf48a7cf0dfcd67aa1a50.png&h=5b0fa484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳說中勇者的結婚活動，爛尾<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/022156_d515ad84126279f1e6bda2eae771c2c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F022156_d515ad84126279f1e6bda2eae771c2c8.png&h=2a4344d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終進化少年<br />\n最後又係變左王道少年漫...明明一開始仲話要探討生死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/19/023312_f48bfef56f72e4d09ac01a78f17aec49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F19%2F023312_f48bfef56f72e4d09ac01a78f17aec49.png&h=d15251d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後係多人睇少少既，廢事貼圖：<br />\n高分少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n測不準的阿波連同學<br />\n植木的法則<br />\n武士佛朗明哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢套真係好啱我電波<br />\n貓湯<br />\n照明商店（明明唔睇恐怖漫，但開左個頭，唔知個尾就更加驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n暫時記得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來只係掃兩下連登，突然變左追漫模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一追就追到天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ea8e1d6269d37722f59b0912b17d68a08d1ec5","tid":633961,"uid":6327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:44:35.000Z","msg":"思春期的誘惑"},{"pid":"c4471c1a7b3a365ecf9adb75f6f696f591375407","tid":633961,"uid":85965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:51:08.000Z","msg":"沖繩奴隸島"},{"pid":"ddd870cda6dc87329d6ec52a21fecfe503fa96e6","tid":633961,"uid":16086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"我的名字是「少年A」"},{"pid":"64cb060888a6c30b040d4f88b2187dc16a340001","tid":633961,"uid":5327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"槍王黑澤"},{"pid":"0dd76a654127e4fd060d6ddfb8a4347551e2f654","tid":633961,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"後遺症無線電"},{"pid":"b9f797246f1edc7b018691bcb939525b9f1e73b3","tid":633961,"uid":65298,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T23:13:03.000Z","msg":"圓周率 &pi;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多年前高登推介"},{"pid":"5de2914e22fc449c3fc6915f9bb33f9ce0efece4","tid":633961,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4471c1a7b3a365ecf9adb75f6f696f5913